To use GetResponse API 2.x with PHP you need JSONRPCPHP library installed.

LIBRARY SOURCE

    http://jsonrpcphp.org/

INSTALLATION

    1. visit http://jsonrpcphp.org/
    2. from Download page get JSON-RCP_PHP_light.zip file
    3. extract jsonrpcphp/includes/jsonRPCClient.php to your project main directory

USAGE

    Remeber to put

        require_once 'jsonRPCClient.php';

    in your script headers.


